                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <surplus>et</surplus> Maximianae Aemiliae et securita<lb break="no" n="2"/>ti eius perpetuae quae <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>os</ex></expan> XXXVII <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Ursino <expan><abbr>dulcissim</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> marito meo in XXX et VIII asce<lb break="no" n="4"/>ndens animam deposui meam vos <expan><abbr>itaq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> Inferi <lb n="5"/>ad quos me praecipitem Di Superi coegerunt minimo cum <lb n="6"/>tormento admittite <expan><abbr>ossaq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> mea in hac arca bene composi<lb break="no" n="7"/>ta condidit <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Ursinus maritus dulcissimus et <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Maximi<lb break="no" n="8"/>anus filius meus et post haec omnia valete <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Ursinus Maxi<lb break="no" n="9"/>mianae Aemiliae <expan><abbr>coniug</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>kariss</abbr><ex>imae</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>castiss</abbr><ex>imae</ex></expan> posui <expan><abbr>vivusq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> feci cum <lb n="10"/>qua vixi <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> XVIIII <expan><abbr>mensib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> VIIII <expan><abbr>poniq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> me post <expan><abbr>mort</abbr><ex>em</ex></expan> meam <lb n="11"/>ab herede meo in hac arc<supplied reason="lost">a iussi</supplied> <lb n="12"/>A<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>I qui et <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">Ma</supplied>xi<lb break="no" n="13"/>miana homo fuit mortua est <lb n="14"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>oc</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>onumentum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eredem</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>on</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>equetur</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sarkophagkasten. Inschriftfeld gerahmt und flankiert von Darstellungen von Amor und Psyche; auf der linken Nebenseite Perseus mit Medusa, auf der rechten mit Andromeda dargestellt. Z. 1: Buchstaben D und M stehen außerhalb der oberen Ecken des Rahmens. Metrik: Z. 4-7: kleine Asklepiadeen; Z. 7-9: Choriamben. (B): CLEPann: Z. 3: XXVII; Z. 4/5: asc/endens; Z. 13: ---] qui; Z. 14; fui.</p>
            </div>
